OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,FITV News US Correspondent Dan Rivers
OL,7,Freports from Washington DC, as more
OL,8,Fdetails of the shooting incident at
OL,9,Fthe Washington Hilton emerge
OL,11,FDonald Trump said he was "not worried"
OL,12,Fwhen a gunman opened fire during a
OL,13,FWhite House event in an apparent
OL,14,Fassassination attempt.
OL,16,FThe president and his wife were
OL,17,Fbundled to safety by Secret Service
OL,18,Fagents on Saturday evening after shots
OL,19,Fwere fired in the lobby of the White
OL,20,FHouse Correspondents' Dinner at the
OL,21,FWashington Hilton Hotel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
