OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,FThe suspect, identified as teacher
OL,7,FCole Tomas Allen, 31, allegedly sent
OL,8,Fmessages to his family describing
OL,9,Fhimself as a "Friendly Federal
OL,10,FAssassin", and voiced grievances about
OL,11,Fthe actions of the US administration.
OL,13,FOne security officer was hit but was
OL,14,Fwearing a bulletproof vest and is
OL,15,Fexpected to make a full recovery.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
