OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,FAsked how concerned he was about
OL,7,Fhearing the gunshots, Trump told CBS
OL,8,FNews: "I wasn't worried. I understand
OL,9,Flife. We live in a crazy world."
OL,11,FThe US president continued that he had
OL,12,Fread a manifesto allegedly written by
OL,13,FAllen, which showed he was "going
OL,14,Fthrough a lot".
OL,16,F"His brother complained about him and
OL,17,FI think reported him to the police.
OL,18,FAnd his sister, likewise, complained
OL,19,Fabout him," Trump said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
