PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777313467
OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,F"His family was very concerned. He was
OL,7,Fprobably a pretty sick guy."
OL,9,FAllen will appear in court on Monday,
OL,10,Fwhere he faces a series of charges,
OL,11,Fincluding attempting to kill a federal
OL,12,Fofficer.
OL,14,FTodd Blanche, acting leader of the US
OL,15,FJustice Department, said on Sunday
OL,16,Fthat it did appear the suspect "set
OL,17,Fout to target folks who work in the
OL,18,Fadministration, likely including the
OL,19,Fpresident".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
