OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,FDuring Trump's CBS News interview,
OL,7,Fjournalist Norah O'Donnell referenced
OL,8,Fwords in Allen's alleged manifesto: "I
OL,9,Fam no longer willing to permit a
OL,10,Fpaedophile, rapist, and traitor to
OL,11,Fcoat my hands with his crimes."
OL,13,FThe president responded to the
OL,14,Finterviewer angrily, reiterating that
OL,15,Fthe suspect was a "sick person" and
OL,16,Ftelling her: "I'm not a rapist. I
OL,17,Fdidn't rape anybody. I'm not a
OL,18,Fpaedophile."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
