OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,FTrump is preparing for a visit from
OL,7,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla on
OL,8,FMonday, which will mark the 250th
OL,9,Fanniversary of American independence.
OL,11,FThe trip is still going ahead despite
OL,12,Fthe shooting, following discussions on
OL,13,Fboth sides of the Atlantic.
OL,15,FCharles and Camilla's first engagement
OL,16,Fwill be a private afternoon tea with
OL,17,FTrump and his wife, Melania, followed
OL,18,Fby a tour of the newly expanded White
OL,19,FHouse Beehive on the South Lawn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
