OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777313467
OL,3,CTrump 'not worried' by shooting as he
OL,4,Cprepares to welcome King Charles
OL,6,F"We are very confident that all
OL,7,Fappropriate security measures are in
OL,8,Fplace," Sir Christian Turner, British
OL,9,Fambassador to the US, said.
OL,11,FTrump said during his CBS News
OL,12,Finterview he thought Charles would be
OL,13,F"very safe", adding: "The White House
OL,14,Fgrounds are really safe."
OL,16,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,18,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,19,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
